                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9138" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0595</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2406 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“绿”力同心：企业-工会关系助推中国建材中复连众企业绿色创新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Green&quot; Synergy: The enterprise-union relationship promotes the evolutionary road of Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise’s green innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡恩华，路文玲，查萱琪（通讯作者），袁潇，张俊婷，徐嫣，方志成，刘星言，李祥发，许虎，梁颖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">连云港中复连众复合材料集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">劳资部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中复连众企业；企业-工会关系；利用式创新；探索式创新；演变；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise, enterprise-union relationship, green exploitative innovation, green exploratory innovation; evolution</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国工会改革的推进，企业和工会双方在推动企业绿色创新方面的独特作用受到关注。本案例以中国建材集团中复连众企业（简称中复连众企业）为案例对象，以企业和工会携手推动企业绿色创新为主线，描述双方在三个阶段内发展出不同的互动关系形态，并助推企业利用式创新与探索式创新呈现出不同的演化特征。2005-2009年间，中复连众企业与工会只能在生产纪律管理、劳动技能竞赛上进行有限互动，使得员工只能被动模仿，绿色创新呈现举步维艰的特征；2010-2019年间，中复连众企业与工会在绿色创新管理决策方面的互动日益深入，企业利用式创新见成效，探索式创新见实效，但由于员工获取的绿色创新资源缺乏稳定持续投入，使企业绿色创新难以为继；2020年以来，中复连众企业与工会之间逐步形成“和合共生”关系，携手为员工构筑起绿色创新管理体系，使得利用式创新和探索式创新实现均衡发展，助力中复连众企业成为国内外风电叶片技术领域的“领航者”。本案例从企业-工会关系互动视角来推动企业绿色创新提供了有益实践指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the advancement of union reform in China, the unique role of enterprises and unions in promoting green innovation in enterprises has been paid attention to. This case, focusing on the China Building Materials Group Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise (the abbreviation for Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise), focusing on the relationship between Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise and union to promote green innovation as the main line. It outlines the distinctive interactive relationships in three stages, each stage showcasing different evolutionary characteristics of green exploitative innovation and green exploratory innovation. From 2005 to 2009, Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise and its union could only have limited interaction in production discipline management and labor skill contests, so that employees could only passively imitate, leaving green innovation in difficulty. From 2010 to2019, the interaction between Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise and union in green innovation management decision-making had deepened, enabling successes in green exploitative innovation and practical results in green exploratory innovation. However, since the green innovation resources available to employees were not stable and continuous, green innovation was hard to sustain. Since 2020, Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise has gradually formed a harmonious and symbiotic relationship with the union. Together they have built a green innovation management system for employees. This has enabled Zhongfu Lianzhong enterprise to achieve balanced development of green exploitative innovation and exploratory innovation, and to become a leader in the field of wind turbine blade technology at home and abroad. This case provides valuables practical guidance for establishing an appropriate enterprise-union relationship to enhance the fulfill of green innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《创新管理》、《劳动关系管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色创新管理；注意力基础观；企业-工会关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
